quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  32,12,"Sinno a yi'atno, tuma nde bon…ďe …ďen ugginta ko'e-ma…ď…ďe ka Joomi ma…ď…ďe! [l∆Āe mbi'a]: "Joomi amen, min nji'ii min nanii, rutton min, min ngolla ko mo∆ī∆īi; minen men njananaama"."
  32,13,"Sinno Min muuyuno, Min ngokkayno kala woŇčkii peewal makki. Ko woni tun, konngol jojjii immorde e An : "Ma Mi hebbiniray Jahannama on jinna e yim…ďe, …ďe denndaangal"."
  32,14,""Mee…óiree (lepte …óen) sabu mbelsindagol mon kawrugol e ndee √Īalaande mon …óoo. Menen (kadi) Men yejjitii on. Mee…óiree lepte luttal, sabu ko ngollatno…óon kon"."
  32,15,"Nganndee ko gooŇč…óinta Aayeeje Amen …óen, ko …ďen taw…ďe si …ďe mbaajoraama …óe, …ďe cuuyiray sujjugol, …ďe subbuhinora jettugol Joomi ma…ď…ďe, kam…ďe …ďe townitotaako."
  32,16,"Becce ma…ď…ďe …óen he…óe ngo…ó…óitoo e lelor…óe …óen, hi…ďe noddira Joomi ma…ď…ďe kulol e …óamaa'mu; e kon ko Min ngarsiki …ďe, hi…ďe mbintoo."
  32,17,"WoŇčkii (woo) anndaa ko maranaa …ďe e ko …ďu…ď…ďinta …ďernde, …óum ko njo…ďdi ko …ďe gollatnoo kon !"
  32,18,"E on laatii…óo gooŇč…óin…óo wa'ay wa on faasiqe? (aa'aa), …ďe potataa."
  32,19,"Si ko …ďen gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďe ngolli golle mo∆ī∆īe, hino woodani …ďe Aljannaaji weerde jipporde, sabu ko…ďe ngollaynoo kon."
  32,20,"Si tawii non ko …ďe faasiqii…ďe, haray femporde …ďen …óon nden, ko ka Yiite: Tuma kala …ďe faalaa jaltugol e magge, …ďe ruttitee e magge, …ďe wi'anee: "Mee…óee lepte Yiite nge pennato…óon ngen"."